(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
(In 1993, Apple made something called the Newton. It had a revolutionary) show newline
(idea: your stuff just exists. You don't save files or open documents.) show newline
(Things float in a soup of objects, and you find them by asking) show newline
(questions.) show newline
() show newline
